    About this item

    • Heavy and Durable: Built to last, this rugs weight and density ensure it stays in place, offering long-lasting performance even in high-traffic areas.
    • Plush and Soft: Sink your feet into the luxurious plush texture, making it the perfect choice for bedrooms and living spaces where comfort is key.
    • Neutral Tones: Soft beige and cream tones bring warmth and sophistication, effortlessly complementing a variety of dcor styles.
    • Abstract Geometric Design: Subtle geometric patterns add just the right amount of visual interest without overpowering the space.
    • Versatile Room Placement: Ideal for living rooms, bedrooms, and offices, this rug enhances the ambiance of any room with its cozy feel and elegant appearance.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
